content.text:
Trigger it instantly. There's no reason to wait — you've already reset the tracker row, so calling the function manually will immediately evaluate the current #1 and send the notification. Waiting 5 minutes just delays the same result with no benefit.

```sql
DELETE FROM hottest_tracker WHERE month_key = to_char(now() at time zone 'UTC', 'YYYY-MM');
SELECT public.check_hottest_post_tracker();
```

Run both right after deploying the updated SQL function.

